</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFF6FFB7FF3D994268B778E1" blockId="27.[151,756,1222,1408]" pageId="27" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis id="78A8EAE1FFF6FFB7FF3D994268C6787F" bold="true" box="[151,459,1286,1310]" pageId="27" pageNumber="41">Stratigraphic distribution:</emphasis>
